
Happy Diwali Website - Dhruva P Gowda

Steps to host on GitHub Pages:

1. Go to https://github.com and login or create an account.
2. Click the "+" icon ‚Üí New Repository.
3. Name the repository: Happy-Diwali-Dhruva
4. Set it to Public ‚Üí Create Repository.
5. Click "Add file" ‚Üí "Upload files"
6. Drag and drop the contents of this ZIP (index.html)
7. Commit changes
8. Go to Settings ‚Üí Pages
   - Branch: main
   - Folder: / (root)
   - Save
9. Wait 1-2 minutes. Your website will be live at:
   https://yourusername.github.io/Happy-Diwali-Dhruva/

Enjoy your Diwali website! üéÜü™î


